metadata.description: Five years before the events of Episode I, Jedi Master Qui-Gon Jinn and his apprentice, Obi-Wan Kenobi, are already legendary for their exploits.  But despite their powers, the Jedi soon realize that it will take more than the Force and lightsabers to survive!
metadata.name: Star Wars: Qui-Gon & Obi-Wan - Last Stand On Ord Mantell
